              },
              "free_text": [
                " The errors are statistical."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A search  was made for the reaction Li-7(gamma,pt)H-3",
                " (Q = 22.28 MeV) in the gamma-ray energy range  23  -",
                " 27  MeV  using  thick  nuclear  emulsion loaded with",
                " isotope Li-7.  The momentum and energy  conservation",
                " laws   were  used  to  identify  the  reaction.  The",
                " integrated reaction cross section in  the  mentioned",
                " energy region was obtained."
              ]
            }
          ],
